  "text": "In what follows we briefly describe the PP GV protocol introduced by Yadav, Srikanth and Pathak [CITATION_1] . We can convert PP protocol to PP GV protocol by modifying steps PP1, PP2 and PP4 of PP protocol described above as follows:",
